description:
Your task is to carefully park large trucks. Each task is a new challenge: you will need to maneuver through narrow passages, avoid obstacles and accurately park your truck in the designated area.

Every situation is unique, and with each level the difficulty increases, forcing you to do everything possible to cope with the task! Parking a large truck is not so easy, especially if it is equipped with a heavy trailer. You will have to show concentration and precision to correctly estimate the distance and turning angle.

Learn to operate heavy equipment and use your skills to avoid penalties for mistakes. In the game you will find different types of trucks and trailers, each of which requires its own approach and driving style. Collect points for fulfilling the conditions and improve your skills, opening new levels and more difficult tasks.

Can you become a master of truck parking? Take the wheel and show other drivers what you are made of!

GAME FEATURES:
• Realistic vehicle control physics;
• Many levels with varying difficulty;
• Large fleet of trucks;
